<SYNC Start=719295><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=748584><P Class=KRCC>
적당히 좀 해라!
<SYNC Start=751745><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=759633><P Class=KRCC>
